                    <li>Give option to minimize to tray when closing from the X button</li>
                    <li>Quit App with Ctrl+Q and hide it with Ctrl+H</li>
                    <li>Renamed parameters `udev-add-rule` and `udev-remove-rule` to `add-udev-rule` and
                        `remove-udev-rule`
                    </li>
                    <li>Several library updates</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
